00:39:18.700 --> 00:39:21.760
And she's the co-editor
of "She's Such a Geek."

00:39:21.760 --> 00:39:23.980
Formerly, she was a policy
analyst for the Electronic

00:39:23.980 --> 00:39:25.610
Frontier Foundation
and a lecturer

00:39:25.610 --> 00:39:27.770
at the University of
California-Berkeley,

00:39:27.770 --> 00:39:32.710
where she received a Ph.D. in
